OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBlustery showers through the
OL,6,Fmorning and early afternoon with some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells, but largely
OL,8,Fcloudy. Becoming dry later in the
OL,9,Fafternoon with long sunny spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Strong westerly winds
OL,11,Feasing later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry start to the evening with
OL,14,Flong clear spells. Turning cloudier
OL,15,Flater in the evening and overnight
OL,16,Fwith few showers possible, but still
OL,17,Fplenty of dry and clear intervals.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
