OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSunny intervals with patchy
OL,6,Fcloud and a few showers in the morning
OL,7,Fbut these dying out to leave a dry
OL,8,Fafternoon with long spells of
OL,9,Fsunshine. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,13,FSunday and Monday as winds strengthen,
OL,14,Fsome drier and brighter intervals
OL,15,Fpossible. Drier on Tuesday with just
OL,16,Fthe odd shower and sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
